00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
秋风萧萧绕古城
Autumn wind whistles 'round the ancient town

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
茶馆巷陌 说书的人
In teahouses and lanes, the storyteller sits

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,000
街角掩庭院深深
Deep courtyards hide 'neath street corners

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:19,000
藏燕青门里几度春秋
Within Yanqing Gate, years come and go

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,000
雨打磨剑痕
Rain polishes the sword's scars

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:27,000
武医心法贯乾坤
Martial and medical wisdom run through heaven and earth

7
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:32,000
他抛洒的热血仍残留温存
The blood he shed still holds a trace of warmth

8
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
曾有故事中的他
Once there was him in tales

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:41,000
义薄云天 风姿潇洒
Righteous above all, graceful and unrestrained

10
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:45,000
燕青引箭生繁花
Yanqing draws the bow, and flowers bloom

11
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:49,000
扶危救困名震天下
Aiding the needy, his fame resounds across the land

12
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:53,000
