Can we find the answer of a true hero?

15
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:06,000
燕青门前十载春夏
Ten springs and autumns before Yanqing Gate

16
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:10,000
武医天术纵横天下
Martial and medical arts prevail across the land

17
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:15,000
为天地 为苍生 为国为家
For heaven and earth, for all living beings, for country and home

18
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:20,000
